- Helm charts for Kubernetes
- Dagger for build automation

### DevSecOps
DevSecOps integrates security practices into the CI/CD pipeline, ensuring that security checks are performed at every stage of the software development lifecycle.
Examples:
- Security scanning in pipelines (SAST/DAST)
- Secret management
